hadiths[41]{hadithnumber,text}:
5897,"abu khaisma ne Aasim ahwal se, unhon-ne Yusuf bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se dam jhaad ke barey mein riwayat bayan ki, kaha : zahreeley dank jild par nikalney waley daanon aur nazare-bad (ke awaariz) mein dam karaaney ki ijazat di gaee hai."
5898,"Sufiyan aur Hasan-bin- Saleh donon ne Aasim unhon-ne Yusuf bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nazar bad , zahreeley dank aur jild par nikalney waley daanon mein dam karne ki ijazat di aur Sufiyan ki riwayat main (yo saf bin-Abdullah ke bajaey) Yusuf bin-Abdullah-bin Haris (se marwi) hai."
5899,"Sufiyan aur Hasan-bin- Saleh donon ne Aasim unhon-ne Yusuf bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nazar bad , zahreeley dank aur jild par nikalney waley daanon mein dam karne ki ijazat di aur Sufiyan ki riwayat main (yo saf bin-Abdullah ke bajaey) Yusuf bin-Abdullah-bin Haris (se marwi) hai."
5900,"Zenab binte-Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bevi Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein aik ladki ke barey mein jiske chehrey (ke aik hissey (ka rang badla hua dekha, farmaya : usko nazar lag gaee hai usko dam karao . aap ki murad iske chehrey ki peelahat se thi."
5901,"Zenab binte-Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bevi Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein aik ladki ke barey mein jiske chehrey (ke aik hissey (ka rang badla hua dekha, farmaya : usko nazar lag gaee hai usko dam karao . aap ki murad iske chehrey ki peelahat se thi."
5902,"abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aal ( banu- Amr bin ( Hazam ko sanp (ke kaatey (ka dam karne ki ijazat di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : kya hua hai main apne bhai (Hazrat Jafar bin abi-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu)) ke bachchon ke jism laaghar dekh raha hun, kya unhein bhookaa rehna padta hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi lekin unhein nazar bad jaldi lag jati hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhein dam karo. unhon ( Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : to maine ( dam ke alfaz ko) aap ke samney pesh kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (un alfaz se) unko dam kar do."
5903,"abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aal ( banu- Amr bin ( Hazam ko sanp (ke kaatey (ka dam karne ki ijazat di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : kya hua hai main apne bhai (Hazrat Jafar bin abi-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu)) ke bachchon ke jism laaghar dekh raha hun, kya unhein bhookaa rehna padta hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi lekin unhein nazar bad jaldi lag jati hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhein dam karo. unhon ( Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : to maine ( dam ke alfaz ko) aap ke samney pesh kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (un alfaz se) unko dam kar do."
5904,"Rooh-bin-Ubada ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Amr (bin-Hazam) ko sanp ke dasney ki sura mein dam karne ki ijazat di. abu-Zubair ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se (ye bhi) suna, wo kehtey they : ham mein se aik shakhs ko bichhoo ne dank mar diya, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they ke aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main dam kar dun? aap ne farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs apne bhai ko fayda pahuncha sakta ho to usey aisa karna chahiye."
5905,"Rooh-bin-Ubada ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Amr (bin-Hazam) ko sanp ke dasney ki sura mein dam karne ki ijazat di. abu-Zubair ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se (ye bhi) suna, wo kehtey they : ham mein se aik shakhs ko bichhoo ne dank mar diya, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they ke aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main dam kar dun? aap ne farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs apne bhai ko fayda pahuncha sakta ho to usey aisa karna chahiye."
5906,Saeed-bin-Yahya umwi ke walid ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki misl riwayat bayan ki magar unhon-ne kaha : logon mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kya main usko dam kar dun? aur (sirf) : dam kar dun nahi kaha.
5907,Saeed-bin-Yahya umwi ke walid ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki misl riwayat bayan ki magar unhon-ne kaha : logon mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kya main usko dam kar dun? aur (sirf) : dam kar dun nahi kaha.
5908,"Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mere aik maamun they wo bichhoo ke kaatey par dam kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (umumi taur se har tarah ke) dam karne se mana farmaya. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap ne dam karne se mana farma diya hai. main bichhoo ke kaatey pe dam karta hun to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo koi apne bhai ko fayda pahuncha sakta ho to wo aisa kare."
5909,"Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mere aik maamun they wo bichhoo ke kaatey par dam kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (umumi taur se har tarah ke) dam karne se mana farmaya. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap ne dam karne se mana farma diya hai. main bichhoo ke kaatey pe dam karta hun to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo koi apne bhai ko fayda pahuncha sakta ho to wo aisa kare."
5910,Jarir ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5911,Jarir ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5912,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dam karne se mana farma diya to Amr-bin-Hazam ka khandan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya, Allah ke rasool ! hamarey paas dam (karne ka aik kalima) tha. ham us se bichhoo ke dasey huey ko dam kartey they aur aap ne dam karne se mana farma diya. unhon ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : to unhon-ne wo pesh kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main (is mein koi) harj nahi samajhta . tum mein se jo koi apne bhai ko fayda pahuncha sakta ho to wo zaroor usey fayda pahunchaaey."
5913,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dam karne se mana farma diya to Amr-bin-Hazam ka khandan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya, Allah ke rasool ! hamarey paas dam (karne ka aik kalima) tha. ham us se bichhoo ke dasey huey ko dam kartey they aur aap ne dam karne se mana farma diya. unhon ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : to unhon-ne wo pesh kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main (is mein koi) harj nahi samajhta . tum mein se jo koi apne bhai ko fayda pahuncha sakta ho to wo zaroor usey fayda pahunchaaey."
5914,"Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : ham zamana jahiliyat mein dam kiya kartey they. ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! uske barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne dam ke kalimaat mere samney pesh karo dam mein koi harj nahi jab tak usmein shirk na ho."
5915,"Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : ham zamana jahiliyat mein dam kiya kartey they. ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! uske barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne dam ke kalimaat mere samney pesh karo dam mein koi harj nahi jab tak usmein shirk na ho."
5916,"Hushaim ne abu Bishr se, unhon-ne abu-mutawakkil se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) safar mein they Arab ke qabaayel mein se kisi qabeeley ke samney se unka guzar hua unhon-ne un (qabeeley waale) logon se chaha ke wo unhein apna mehman banaaein. unhon-ne mehman banaaney se inkar kar diya, phir unhon-ne kaha : kya tum mein koi dam karne wala hai? kyonke qaum ke sardaar ko kisi cheez ne das liya hai ya usey koi bimari laahiq ho gaee hai. un (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : haan phir wo uske qareeb aaey aur usey fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) se dam kar diya. wo aadmi theek ho gaya to us (dam karne waale) ko bakriyon ka ek rewad ( tees bakriyan ( pesh ki gain. us ne unhein (fauri taur par) qabool karne (kaam mein laney) se inkar kar diya aur kaha : yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maajraa suna dun . wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Sara maajraa aapko sunaya aur kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maine fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) ke ilawa aur koi dam nahi kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : tumhen kaisey pata chala ke wo dam (bhi) hai? phir unhein ley lo aur apne sath mera bhi hissey rakho."
5917,"Hushaim ne abu Bishr se, unhon-ne abu-mutawakkil se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) safar mein they Arab ke qabaayel mein se kisi qabeeley ke samney se unka guzar hua unhon-ne un (qabeeley waale) logon se chaha ke wo unhein apna mehman banaaein. unhon-ne mehman banaaney se inkar kar diya, phir unhon-ne kaha : kya tum mein koi dam karne wala hai? kyonke qaum ke sardaar ko kisi cheez ne das liya hai ya usey koi bimari laahiq ho gaee hai. un (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : haan phir wo uske qareeb aaey aur usey fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) se dam kar diya. wo aadmi theek ho gaya to us (dam karne waale) ko bakriyon ka ek rewad ( tees bakriyan ( pesh ki gain. us ne unhein (fauri taur par) qabool karne (kaam mein laney) se inkar kar diya aur kaha : yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maajraa suna dun . wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Sara maajraa aapko sunaya aur kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maine fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) ke ilawa aur koi dam nahi kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : tumhen kaisey pata chala ke wo dam (bhi) hai? phir unhein ley lo aur apne sath mera bhi hissey rakho."
5918,"Shoba ne abu Bishr se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, aur hadis mein ye kaha is ne Ummul-Quran (sura Fatiha) padhni shuru ki aur apna thook jama karta aur is par phainktaa jata to wo aadmi tandurust ho gaya."
5919,"Shoba ne abu Bishr se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, aur hadis mein ye kaha is ne Ummul-Quran (sura Fatiha) padhni shuru ki aur apna thook jama karta aur is par phainktaa jata to wo aadmi tandurust ho gaya."
5920,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Hassan ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se khabar di, unhon-ne apne bhai Mabad-bin-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se, riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne aik maqam par padaaw kiya , aik aurat hamarey paas aai aur kaha : qabeeley ke sardaar ko dank laga hai, ( usey bichho ne dank maara hai) kya tum mein se koi dam karne wala hai? ham mein se aik aadmi uske sath ( janey ke liye) khada ho gaya. uske barey mein hamara khayal nahi tha ke wo achi tarah dam kar sakta hai. us ne us (dasey huey) ko Fatiha se dam kiya to wo theek ho gaya, to unhon-ne usey bakriyon ka aik rewad diya aur ham sab ko doodh pilaya. ham ne (us se) puchha : kya tum achi tarah dam karna jantey they? usne kaha : maine usey sirf fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) se dam kiya hai. kaha : maine (sathiyon se) kaha : un bakriyon ko kuchh na kaho yahan tak ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho jaaein. ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, aapko ye baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey kis zariey se pata chala ke ye ( Fatiha ( dam (ka kalima bhi) hai? un (bakriyon) ko baant lo aur apne sath mera bhi hissey rakho."
5921,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Hassan ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se khabar di, unhon-ne apne bhai Mabad-bin-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se, riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne aik maqam par padaaw kiya , aik aurat hamarey paas aai aur kaha : qabeeley ke sardaar ko dank laga hai, ( usey bichho ne dank maara hai) kya tum mein se koi dam karne wala hai? ham mein se aik aadmi uske sath ( janey ke liye) khada ho gaya. uske barey mein hamara khayal nahi tha ke wo achi tarah dam kar sakta hai. us ne us (dasey huey) ko Fatiha se dam kiya to wo theek ho gaya, to unhon-ne usey bakriyon ka aik rewad diya aur ham sab ko doodh pilaya. ham ne (us se) puchha : kya tum achi tarah dam karna jantey they? usne kaha : maine usey sirf fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) se dam kiya hai. kaha : maine (sathiyon se) kaha : un bakriyon ko kuchh na kaho yahan tak ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho jaaein. ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, aapko ye baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey kis zariey se pata chala ke ye ( Fatiha ( dam (ka kalima bhi) hai? un (bakriyon) ko baant lo aur apne sath mera bhi hissey rakho."
5922,"hamein Hisham ne isi sanad ke sath , isi tarah hadis bayan ki, magar usne kaha : ham mein se aik aadmi uske sath (janey ke liye khada ho gaya) ham ne kabhi guman nahi kiya tha ke wo dam kar sakta hai."
5923,"hamein Hisham ne isi sanad ke sath , isi tarah hadis bayan ki, magar usne kaha : ham mein se aik aadmi uske sath (janey ke liye khada ho gaya) ham ne kabhi guman nahi kiya tha ke wo dam kar sakta hai."
5924,"saiyedna Usman-bin-abi-al-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne aik dard ki shikayat ki, jo unke badan mein paida ho gaya tha jab se wo musalman huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apna hath dard ki jagah par rakho aur teen baar ( bismillaah ( kaho , iske baad saat (7) baar ye kaho :                                                                                                                                   (اَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ وَقُدْرَتِهِ مِنْ شَرِّ ما أَجِدُ وَأُحَاذِرُ)                                                                                                                                         ''main Allah Taala ki panah mangta hun us cheez ki burai se jis ko paata hun aur jis se darta hun.''"
5925,"saiyedna Usman-bin-abi-al-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne aik dard ki shikayat ki, jo unke badan mein paida ho gaya tha jab se wo musalman huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apna hath dard ki jagah par rakho aur teen baar ( bismillaah ( kaho , iske baad saat (7) baar ye kaho :                                                                                                                                   (اَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ وَقُدْرَتِهِ مِنْ شَرِّ ما أَجِدُ وَأُحَاذِرُ)                                                                                                                                         ''main Allah Taala ki panah mangta hun us cheez ki burai se jis ko paata hun aur jis se darta hun.''"
5926,"Abdul-Aala ne Saeed Jurairi se, unhon-ne abul-Ala se riwayat ki ke saiyedna Usman-bin-abul-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! shaitan meri Namaz mein haail (rukaawat) ho jata hai aur mujhey Quran bhula deta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shaitan ka naam khinzab hai. jab tujhey us shaitan ka asar malum ho to us se Allah Taala ki panah maang aur (namaz ke andar hi) baain taraf teen baar thook (thuthkar) ley. saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine aisa hi kiya, phir Allah Taala ne us shaitan ko mujh se door kar diya."
5927,"Abdul-Aala ne Saeed Jurairi se, unhon-ne abul-Ala se riwayat ki ke saiyedna Usman-bin-abul-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! shaitan meri Namaz mein haail (rukaawat) ho jata hai aur mujhey Quran bhula deta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shaitan ka naam khinzab hai. jab tujhey us shaitan ka asar malum ho to us se Allah Taala ki panah maang aur (namaz ke andar hi) baain taraf teen baar thook (thuthkar) ley. saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine aisa hi kiya, phir Allah Taala ne us shaitan ko mujh se door kar diya."
5928,"Saalim-bin Nuh aur abu-Usama, donon ne Jurairi se, unhon-ne Abu Ala se, unhon-ne Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey, phir is tarah bayan kya aur Saalim-bin Nuh ki hadis mein teen baar ka lafz nahi hai."
5929,"Saalim-bin Nuh aur abu-Usama, donon ne Jurairi se, unhon-ne Abu Ala se, unhon-ne Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey, phir is tarah bayan kya aur Saalim-bin Nuh ki hadis mein teen baar ka lafz nahi hai."
5930,"Sufiyan ne Saeed Jurairi se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin Shikhkhir ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir unki hadis ki manind (tarah) bayan kya."
5931,"Sufiyan ne Saeed Jurairi se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin Shikhkhir ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir unki hadis ki manind (tarah) bayan kya."
5932,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har bimari ki dawaa hai, jab koi dawa bimari par theek bitha di jati hai to mareez Allah Taala ke hukm se tandurust ho jata hai."
5933,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har bimari ki dawaa hai, jab koi dawa bimari par theek bitha di jati hai to mareez Allah Taala ke hukm se tandurust ho jata hai."
5934,"Bukair ne kaha ke Aasim bin Umar-bin Qatada ne unhein hadis sunai ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne miqna (bin Sanan taabai ( ki iyaadat ki, phir farmaya : main (is waqt tak) yahan se nahi jaaunga jab tak ke tum pachhney na lagwaa lo, kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey hain : yaqinan usmein shifa hai."
5935,"Bukair ne kaha ke Aasim bin Umar-bin Qatada ne unhein hadis sunai ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne miqna (bin Sanan taabai ( ki iyaadat ki, phir farmaya : main (is waqt tak) yahan se nahi jaaunga jab tak ke tum pachhney na lagwaa lo, kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey hain : yaqinan usmein shifa hai."
5936,"Abdur-Rehman bin Sulaiman ne Hazrat Aasim bin Umar-bin Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : ke saiyedna Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey ghar mein aaey aur aik shakhs ko zakhm ki takleef thi (yani qarha pad gaya tha). saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tujhey kya takleef hai? wo bola ke aik zakhm ho gaya hai jo ke mujh par bahut hi zyada sakht hai. saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aey ghulam ! aik pachhney lagaaney waley ko lekar aa . wo bola ke pachhney lagaaney waley ka kya kaam hai? saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main us zakhm par pachhney lagwaana chahta hun, wo bola ke Allah ki qism mujhey makkhiyaan sataaein gii aur kapda lagega to mujhey takleef hogi aur mujh par bahut sakht ( waqt) guzrega. jab saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke usko pachhney lagaaney se ranj hota hai to kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke agar tumhari dawaaon mein behtar koi dawa hai to teen hi dawaaein hain, aik to pachhna, doosra shehad ka aik ghoont aur tesraa angaarey se jalaana aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main dagh lena behtar nahi janta. rawi ne kaha ke phir pachhney lagaaney wala aaya aur us ne usko pachhney lagaey aur uski bimari jati rahi."
5937,"Abdur-Rehman bin Sulaiman ne Hazrat Aasim bin Umar-bin Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : ke saiyedna Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey ghar mein aaey aur aik shakhs ko zakhm ki takleef thi (yani qarha pad gaya tha). saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tujhey kya takleef hai? wo bola ke aik zakhm ho gaya hai jo ke mujh par bahut hi zyada sakht hai. saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aey ghulam ! aik pachhney lagaaney waley ko lekar aa . wo bola ke pachhney lagaaney waley ka kya kaam hai? saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main us zakhm par pachhney lagwaana chahta hun, wo bola ke Allah ki qism mujhey makkhiyaan sataaein gii aur kapda lagega to mujhey takleef hogi aur mujh par bahut sakht ( waqt) guzrega. jab saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke usko pachhney lagaaney se ranj hota hai to kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke agar tumhari dawaaon mein behtar koi dawa hai to teen hi dawaaein hain, aik to pachhna, doosra shehad ka aik ghoont aur tesraa angaarey se jalaana aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main dagh lena behtar nahi janta. rawi ne kaha ke phir pachhney lagaaney wala aaya aur us ne usko pachhney lagaey aur uski bimari jati rahi."
